Source: kickseed
Section: debian-installer
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Colin Watson <cjwatson@ubuntu.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 4.2), dpkg-dev (>= 1.9)
Standards-Version: 3.6.1

Package: kickseed-common
XC-Package-Type: udeb
Architecture: all
Priority: standard
Description: Common files for Kickstart compatibility
 This package reads Kickstart files and preseeds an installation with them,
 translating to the d-i preseeding infrastructure.

Package: initrd-kickseed
XC-Package-Type: udeb
Architecture: all
Depends: kickseed-common, preseed-common
Description: Load Kickstart file from the initrd

Package: file-kickseed
XC-Package-Type: udeb
XB-Installer-Menu-Item: 14
Architecture: all
Depends: kickseed-common, preseed-common
Description: Load Kickstart file from CD-ROM or floppy disk

Package: network-kickseed
XC-Package-Type: udeb
XB-Installer-Menu-Item: 21
Architecture: all
Depends: kickseed-common, preseed-common
Description: Download Kickstart file
